Look forward to share my passion to the night sky with the participants at Maine Stargazing & Photography Retreat on Aug 28 - Sep 1, a program open to all enthusiasts at any level, a few hours drives north of Boston in a dark sky protected site. We have a number of guest speakers including world-known NatGeo & BBC wildlife photographer @timlaman and his son @russlaman who will share their truly inspiring stories. To learn more tap the link in my bio, or visit babaktafreshi.com/maine. 
The 4-night all-inclusive retreat includes workshops for both hobby and pro photographers, stargazing lessons and enjoying the view through our telescopes. In day-time we have lecture, nature walks and kayaking, hosted in the wonderful @medomakcamp, next to a pristine lake. 
